You are running two ARCWriters in the same crawler?   You may have 
uncovered an issue in the pooling code.  The two instances may be 
interfering w/ each other.  Otherwise, Disks are healthy Olaf?  They are 
not full and dmesg output isn&#39;t complaining that its having trouble 
writing a particular disk?  You might also provoke a thread dump. Look 
at the output in heritrix_out to see if you can identify where the 
checked out ARCWriters are stuck.

St.Ack


